<section class="container">
  <h1>M2M Authentication Demo</h1>
  <p>Request a token using Client Credentials, then call a protected API route with the bearer token.</p>

  <h2>Token Request</h2>
  <pre><code>POST <%= @example_token_request[:url] %>
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

<%= URI.encode_www_form(@example_token_request[:body]) %></code></pre>

  <h2>Call Protected API</h2>
  <pre><code>GET /api/v1/protected
Authorization: Bearer &lt;access_token&gt;</code></pre>

  <p>This endpoint requires a valid bearer token from the client credentials flow above.</p>
</section>
